PrecisAppointment of RAYMOND DESROCHERS of Winnipeg, Manitoba, selected from a list of nominees submitted by the Province of Manitoba, to be a director of the Board of Management of the Canada Customs and Revenue Agency, to hold office during pleasure for a term of three years.
